title: The Harsh Meaning Behind Mixed Signals in Dating with Case Kenny
description: Hi everyone! Today, we have on Case Kenny to talk about how read mix signals and how to enjoy being single. It may not be as easy as others make it seem, so we will be giving some good pointers on how to read the signals and why it is so important.  Casey's Instagram: @case.kenny His podcast: https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/new-mindset-who-dis/id1383599078 --- Send in a voice message: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy/message Support this podcast: https://anchor.fm/happyandhealthy/support
